## Checklist before sharing

- [ ] Brand name and colors match your agency
- [ ] Client name on the report is correct (or clearly marked as sample)
- [ ] Health score and actions make sense for the site
- [ ] Top 3 actions are understandable without technical explanation
- [ ] Supporting warnings are not the main sales message
- [ ] You have a short cover message (see outreach_messages.md)
- [ ] Proposal ready if the conversation moves to pricing
